## Architectural Rules
- Workflows MUST be deterministic.
- Transition types MUST follow the pipeline.
- Schedules MUST be persistent.
- Orchestration MUST not depend on Execution internals.
- Execution MAY scale independently.

## Multi-Schema Architecture Rules
- Resolve schema through ICurrentSchema.
- Sources: headers, routes, query string, custom resolvers.

## OpenTelemetry
- Start Activity for major operations.
- Logs must include runtimeKey, domain, correlation ID.

## Result Pattern & Error Handling
- Use Result<T> for business ops.
- Exceptions only for infrastructure failures.

## Background Services
- Use BackgroundService for task processors.
- Use IHostedService for lifecycle control.


Follow the official Microsoft documentation and ASP.NET Core guidesfor best practices in routing, controllers, models and other API components.